00:10:40.350 --> 00:10:42.390
[PD: Welcome to the first mission]

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:42.520
This mission is called
"Press the Shutter, Escape Alive."

00:10:42.520 --> 00:10:44.300
[PD: This task is called]

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:46.600
["Press the Shutter, Escape Alive"]

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:49.700
[Press the Shutter, Escape Alive Mission]

00:10:49.700 --> 00:10:52.960
Press the Shutter, Escape Alive Rule.

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:57.890
Each match must jump onto the trampoline.

00:10:58.250 --> 00:11:03.970
Once one agent successfully
grabs and puts on the hanging relic,

00:11:04.300 --> 00:11:07.120
the 10-second countdown will begin.

00:11:07.850 --> 00:11:11.870
At the exact moment the countdown ends,
the camera shutter will snap immediately.

00:11:11.870 --> 00:11:13.220
Whoever can jump up

00:11:13.220 --> 00:11:17.400
and keep their eyes, nose, mouth—
their entire face—inside the frame

00:11:17.750 --> 00:11:18.450
will be the winner.

00:11:18.450 --> 00:11:19.450
