Ice: We have to wait for them to come out.
They're in now.

01:33:26.140 --> 01:33:29.820
[If there are 2 or more Ghosts,
the elevator will go up to the fourth floor]

01:33:30.460 --> 01:33:33.900
[Which floor will the elevator stop at?]

01:33:36.860 --> 01:33:38.380
[Which floor will the elevator open on?]

01:33:38.400 --> 01:33:38.800
Phuak: That means among us…

01:33:38.800 --> 01:33:40.080
[The elevator doesn't move
and stays on the first floor]

01:33:40.080 --> 01:33:42.560
-It means...
-There're than 2 Ghosts.

01:33:43.160 --> 01:33:44.440
NuNew: That means there are
fewer than 2 ghosts among us.

01:33:44.440 --> 01:33:45.720
So one of us is a ghost, right?

01:33:45.720 --> 01:33:46.280
Phuak: Maybe 1.

01:33:46.280 --> 01:33:48.060
Oat: But I pressed the fourth floor.

01:33:48.060 --> 01:33:50.420
[Among the three of them, two are wizards.]

01:33:50.540 --> 01:33:51.980
Phuak: I eliminated Nont.
Phuak: I eliminated Nont.

01:33:51.980 --> 01:33:54.020
Phuak: I eliminated Nont
with my own hands.

01:33:54.020 --> 01:33:54.980
Phuak: I eliminated Nont.

01:33:54.980 --> 01:33:55.180
[I eliminated Nont]

01:33:55.180 --> 01:33:57.580
Phuak: I eliminated Nont
with my own hands.

01:33:57.620 --> 01:33:59.380
NuNew: Phuak said he eliminated Nont.

01:33:59.380 --> 01:34:00.540
Goy: That's what we just said.

01:34:00.540 --> 01:34:00.620
[Oat: I ripped it off. It was me.]

01:34:00.620 --> 01:34:02.280
Oat: I ripped it off. It was me.

01:34:02.300 --> 01:34:04.140
Oat: I ripped it off. It was me.

01:34:04.780 --> 01:34:05.060
Phuak: I'm so nervous.

01:34:05.060 --> 01:34:09.980
[Between Phuak and Oat,
who is the wizard?]

01:34:10.160 --> 01:34:11.820
Oat: Sir, where's my best friend?

01:34:11.820 --> 01:34:14.550
Oat: Sir, let's go. Let's keep looking for clues.

01:34:14.860 --> 01:34:16.980
[Oat is looking for clues again]

01:34:17.380 --> 01:34:19.740
[Who is the wizard?]

01:34:19.870 --> 01:34:20.220
Phuak: If I speed up chasing Oat,
everything will be over, right?

01:34:20.220 --> 01:34:22.700
[Phuak thinks Oat is the Ghost
and he himself is the wizard]

01:34:23.270 --> 01:34:25.270
-Yes, the game will be over.
-Right?

01:34:26.390 --> 01:34:28.450
-Then I'll just run.
-Just like that?

01:34:29.020 --> 01:34:32.780
Goy: Are you 100% sure?
[Let's see who's a wizard]

01:34:36.740 --> 01:34:40.020
[A confrontation between 2 people
who call themselves wizards]

01:34:41.500 --> 01:34:42.300
Oat: What?

01:34:43.420 --> 01:34:43.700
Phuak: Nothing.

01:34:43.700 --> 01:34:44.580
[A tense psychological battle]

01:34:44.580 --> 01:34:47.310
-What? What are you laughing at?
-Watch the door.

01:34:47.840 --> 01:34:49.110
-Waiting for getting outside.
-What are you laughing at?

01:34:49.110 --> 01:34:50.260
Phuak: Ghosts can't
rip off anyone's name tag.

01:34:50.260 --> 01:34:51.750
[Confused by the mind games
between the seniors]

01:34:51.750 --> 01:34:53.890
-Right. OK.
-Yes.

01:34:53.950 --> 01:34:54.380
Oat: I won't risk ripping your name tag.

01:34:54.380 --> 01:34:55.740
[If a wizard rips another wizard's name tag,
the game ends immediately]

01:34:55.740 --> 01:34:57.190
-Yes, yes.
-Because you are...

01:34:57.190 --> 01:34:58.910
-I could take the risk.
-But the game would end.

01:34:58.910 --> 01:34:59.910
Phuak: Then let it end.

01:34:59.910 --> 01:35:01.630
Phuak: Let’s end it. Oat. End it.

01:35:01.630 --> 01:35:01.860
Phuak: Let's end it, Oat.

01:35:01.860 --> 01:35:05.140
[One careless move will end the game]

01:35:10.880 --> 01:35:12.900
-Come on.
-The exit door is open.

01:35:14.260 --> 01:35:16.120
[The door is open]

01:35:16.120 --> 01:35:17.760
The exit door is open.

01:35:24.150 --> 01:35:25.980
[Oat rushes to the exit]

01:35:25.980 --> 01:35:26.620
Oat: Darn it.

01:35:26.620 --> 01:35:30.060
[Oat runs to the exit,
and Phuak instantly chases after him]

01:35:30.620 --> 01:35:33.860
Phuak: Got you! Got you!
[The name tag is caught
at a critical moment]

01:35:34.620 --> 01:35:35.260
[Run to stop the battle first]

01:35:35.260 --> 01:35:39.020
-Wait.
-Wait.

01:35:39.380 --> 01:35:39.700
[Phuak's name tag is also
at risk of being ripped off]

01:35:39.700 --> 01:35:42.180
-Wait.
-Wait.

01:35:44.420 --> 01:35:46.420
[Wait]
-Wait.
-Calm down.

01:35:46.420 --> 01:35:50.420
Ice: We can talk first.
The two of us are going out now.

01:35:50.420 --> 01:35:51.860
-NuNew's identity is already confirmed.
-We can choose.

01:35:51.860 --> 01:35:54.500
-NuNew is...
-Don't rip it off for now. Wait. Calm down.

01:35:54.500 --> 01:35:56.860
-It'll be over if you make a mistake.
-OK.

01:35:56.860 --> 01:35:56.940
[Decides to keep things
under control for now]

01:35:56.940 --> 01:35:59.060
-Let go, OK?
-Let go. Let go.

01:35:59.060 --> 01:36:00.580
-1, 2, 3.
-1, 2, 3.

01:36:01.280 --> 01:36:02.020
-OK.
-OK.

01:36:02.020 --> 01:36:03.320
NuNew. Listen to me.

01:36:03.320 --> 01:36:07.210
-No. So NuNew is the first one to go out, right?
-Yes.

01:36:07.210 --> 01:36:09.040
NuNew: Then I...

01:36:09.040 --> 01:36:09.840
Ice: Then NuNew…

01:36:09.840 --> 01:36:13.170
-Chooses to hold...
-NuNew chooses to hold another person.

01:36:13.700 --> 01:36:15.180
[Now NuNew must choose
someone to leave with]

01:36:15.180 --> 01:36:19.540
[Will the person NuNew chooses to
go out with be a wizard or a Ghost?]

01:36:21.220 --> 01:36:24.420
[Who does NuNew think the wizard is?]

01:36:24.420 --> 01:36:26.460
-Believe in yourself.
-We have to go.

01:36:26.460 --> 01:36:27.620
NuNew: I choose...

01:36:28.020 --> 01:36:29.700
Let's go. It's almost time. Let's go.
[Who was taken out the door?]

01:36:29.700 --> 01:36:31.110
Let’s go. Run. Run.

01:36:31.140 --> 01:36:33.700
[Wizard NuNew chose Oat]

01:36:38.940 --> 01:36:42.100
[Was NuNew's choice correct?]

01:36:42.100 --> 01:36:44.030
NuNew: Why are you turning around?

01:36:48.180 --> 01:36:53.780
-The name tag ghost-hunting operation is over.
-Yes.

01:36:53.780 --> 01:36:55.940
It’s time to reveal everyone's identity.

01:36:55.940 --> 01:36:57.500
NuNew: But he…

01:36:58.540 --> 01:37:00.740
-Come on, Oat, turn around.
-What are you, Oat?

01:37:00.740 --> 01:37:02.020
[What is Oat's true identity?]

01:37:02.020 --> 01:37:03.380
Oat, turn around.

01:37:11.240 --> 01:37:12.100
Ghost.

01:37:12.100 --> 01:37:14.130
[Oat is a Ghost]

01:37:14.130 --> 01:37:16.160
Ghost.

01:37:16.980 --> 01:37:19.260
[NuNew chose the wrong one,
so the Ghost team wins]

01:37:19.260 --> 01:37:21.580
-Thank you, Oat.
-New blocked it.

01:37:23.460 --> 01:37:27.420
[I told you it's not Oat]

01:37:28.660 --> 01:37:28.940
Nont: Really? You're a Ghost too?

01:37:28.940 --> 01:37:29.740
[Even the Ghosts don't know
each other's identities]

01:37:29.740 --> 01:37:31.620
-I'm a Ghost too.
-Really?

01:37:35.660 --> 01:37:37.300
Jeff: Because I'm a Ghost.

01:37:37.300 --> 01:37:39.500
[Ghost]

01:37:40.420 --> 01:37:41.820
Jeff: It'll be fun today.

01:37:44.980 --> 01:37:47.480
Oat: Have you seen a fierce Ghost?
How can I not be fierce?

01:37:47.480 --> 01:37:50.010
Didn't you see that I died
when I was pregnant?

01:37:53.340 --> 01:37:53.450
[Ghost]

01:37:53.450 --> 01:37:54.250
Goy: OK.

01:37:54.850 --> 01:37:58.450
Goy: I’m not good at lying.
So I have to believe that I'm the wizard.

01:37:58.450 --> 01:37:59.680
Goy: A wizard.

01:38:01.930 --> 01:38:02.730
Ice: Wow.

01:38:03.290 --> 01:38:07.960
Ice: We have to pretend to be shocked.
Make the others think

01:38:08.090 --> 01:38:11.280
