01:38:12.300 --> 01:38:15.980
[Ink, Nont, Jeff, Goy, Ice,
and Oat are Ghosts]

01:38:16.500 --> 01:38:17.540
-Jeff.
-Yeah?

01:38:17.980 --> 01:38:18.060
-Let me ask you like a man.
-OK.

01:38:18.060 --> 01:38:20.700
[By halftime, the two had already
realized they were both ghosts]

01:38:20.700 --> 01:38:23.540
-Are you a Ghost?
-Yes.

01:38:24.140 --> 01:38:24.900
[Oat lied that he had already
eliminated Ghost Nont]

01:38:24.900 --> 01:38:27.260
Goy: He said he ripped it off, not you.

01:38:27.260 --> 01:38:30.580
Oat: I did. I did. It was me.

01:38:32.020 --> 01:38:36.140
[The one who took them out
was Wizard Phuak]

01:38:36.140 --> 01:38:38.540
Nont: Did you just rip
my name tag like that?

01:38:41.510 --> 01:38:42.650
[Phuak's sincere confession]

01:38:42.650 --> 01:38:45.050
Phuak: I eliminated Nont with my own hands.

01:38:45.060 --> 01:38:47.460
Phuak: I eliminated Nont with my own hands.

01:38:48.060 --> 01:38:48.300
[Even though he desperately begged NuNew,
telling him that he was also a wizard,]

01:38:48.300 --> 01:38:52.140
Phuak: We are going to be together.
Because it must be the two of us.

01:38:55.300 --> 01:38:55.500
[he still lost]

01:38:55.500 --> 01:38:56.700
Phuak: Don't ask me.

01:38:57.700 --> 01:38:58.460
Haha.

01:38:58.970 --> 01:39:00.210
You're already amazing.

01:39:00.210 --> 01:39:02.670
-Wizards don't talk much.
-That's amazing.

01:39:02.740 --> 01:39:06.580
-Phuak was acting suspicious.
-I lost everything.

01:39:06.840 --> 01:39:08.720
NuNew: He was acting suspicious.

01:39:09.620 --> 01:39:09.680
[The gold brooch goes to the winning Ghost Team]

01:39:09.680 --> 01:39:12.220
-We didn't get it, Phuak.
-What is it?

01:39:15.700 --> 01:39:19.540
Ink: It's easy to win.

01:39:19.540 --> 01:39:20.100
Oat: Please keep supporting Running Man Thailand.
Never Stop Running.

